freezing works
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an abattoir or factory where livestock are slaughtered and their carcasses frozen


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: rare early use freezing work
